        <trans-unit id="120" translate="yes" xml:space="preserve">
          <source>You can call the <bpt id="p1">[</bpt>GetDeferral<ept id="p1">](../windows/deferrableeventargs-getdeferral-method.md)</ept> method to get the <bpt id="p2">[</bpt>Deferral<ept id="p2">](http://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?LinkId=526520)</ept> object from which you can get all the information about the deferred event.</source>
