          <source>You should then call <bpt id="p1">[</bpt>InvokeAllFinished<ept id="p1">](../windows/deferrableeventargs-invokeallfinished-method.md)</ept> at the end of the event handler method, which ensures that the completion of all deferred events is communicated properly.</source>
